To see all tables inside practice_db:

USE practice_db;

SHOW TABLES;

To see all data from each table:

SELECT * FROM courses;

SELECT * FROM enrollments;

SELECT * FROM university_students;

To see table structure (columns, datatype, primary key, etc.):

DESCRIBE courses;

DESCRIBE enrollments;

DESCRIBE university_students;

To see everything step-by-step in phpMyAdmin:

Click practice_db
Click table name (courses)
Click Browse tab → shows all rows
Click Structure tab → shows columns and keys

